metadata.name: Eonos #1/5
metadata.description: The war in the Eonos universe was a struggle for the safety of different universes. Dark forces were trying to increase their power by capturing the energies of other universes. Therefore, the Guardians gathered together in the Eonos Universe and started a war against the dark forces. The armies of the dark forces outnumbered the Guardians and were supported by monsters, each with different powers.
